                            <comment id="13943832" author="atm" created="Sat, 22 Mar 2014 01:32:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Straightforward patch attached to specify the correct name type for this principal, which will cause the JDK Kerberos library to use the domain_realm mapping to determine the correct realm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No tests are included because of the difficulty of setting up an appropriate environment in the unit tests. I manually tested this and confirmed that it works as expected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
